profile:
Everything H2O is a full service Hot Tub company and water filtration company. We offer 3 different brands of Hot Tubs to choose from. The exclusive NEW La-Z-Boy hot tubs with Aqua Flex under water Recliners, Hydro-Pool self cleaning hot tubs, and Softubs the portable indoor/outdoor hot tubs. We carry a wide range of hot tub accessories and chemicals for all your needs. We provide FREE water testing and offer delivery service of chemicals for our customers. We also provide full service and Warranties on all our hot tubs and equipment.
 
We also offer Residential/Commercial water filtration systems. We carry a large selection of water softeners, iron/sulfur removal systems and Reverse Osmosis drinking systems. We also offer repair and service on existing water conditioning systems. FREE in home water testing for wells or municipal water is available. 
Please contact us for a free water test and quote today!
